tagline: Showing your underscore can be embarassing, put on some underwear.
body:
### Underwear.js.
[Underscore.js](http://underscorejs.org/) is a great library, but I prefer to extend the native prototypes with these types of methods. With Underwear.js, I can use the awesomeness of underscore from the comfort of my own objects.
